Package: ferols
Type: Package
Title: Fixed-Effects Robust OLS via IRLS (Huber M)
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Joachim", "Gassen", role = c("aut", "cre"), 
    email = "gassen@wiwi.hu-berlin.de",
    comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-4364-2911"))
Description: Tools for estimating fixed-effects linear models using 
  Huber M-estimation via iteratively reweighted least squares (IRLS). The 
  package builds on the 'fixest' framework to absorb high-dimensional fixed 
  effects and provides robust sandwich variance estimators with fixest-style 
  interfaces. This is work-in-progress research software; the API and numerical 
  behavior may change.
